null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013181, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "All praise be to Allah Who has honored me with the recognition of Him, the recognition of His Messenger, and the recognition of him the obedience to whom has been made incumbent upon me by Him on account of His mercy to me, His favor that He bestowed upon me, and His conferral upon me with faith. All praise be to Allah Who has allowed me to enter the shrine of His Messenger’s brother and has made me see this shrine while I enjoy good health. All praise be to Allah Who has included me with the visitors of the tomb of His Messenger’s successor.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Hamd Khuda ke liye hai jis ne apni maarefat aur apne Rasool (s.a.w.a) ki maarefat se mujhe izzat di, woh jis ne mujh par rehmat farmaate huwe aur mujh par ehsaan karte huwe apni ita’at mujh par waajib thairaayi aur imaan de kar mujh par maher-baani farmaayi. Hamd Allah ke liye hai jis ne mujh ko apne Nabi (s.a.w.a) ke bhai ke haram mein daakhil kiya aur amn ke saath yeh jagah dikhaayi. Hamd Allah ke liye hai jis ne mujhe Wasiye Rasool ke rauze ke zaaereen mein qaraar diya.", "Urdu": "حمد خداکے لئے ہے جس نے اپنی معرفت اور اپنے رسولؐ کی معرفت سے مجھے عزّت دی وہ جس نے مجھ پر رحمت فرماتے ہوئے اور مجھ پر احسان کرتے ہوئے اپنی اطاعت مجھ پر واجب ٹھہرائی اور ایمان دے کر مجھ پر مہربانی فرمائی حمد اللہ کے لئے ہے جس نے مجھ کو اپنے نبیؐ کے بھائی کے حرم میں داخل کیا اور امن کے ساتھ یہ جگہ دکھائی حمد اللہ کے لئے ہے جس نے مجھے وصی ؑرسولؐ کے روضہ کے زائرین میں قرار دیا۔", "RArabic": "ALHAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE AKRAMA-NEE BEMA’RE-FATEHI WA MA’REFATE RASOOLE-HI WA MAN FARAZA A’LAIYYA TAA-A’TA-HU RAHMATAM MINHO LEE WA TATAWWO-LAM MINHO A’LAIYYA WA MANNA A’LAIYYA BIL EEMAA-NE ALHAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE AD-KHALA-NEE HARAMA AKHEE RASOOLE-HI WA ARAANEE-HE FEE AA’FE-YATIN ALHAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE JA-A’LANEE MIN ZUWWAARE QABRE WASIYYE RASOOLE-HI.", "ArabicText1": "اَلْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِیْ اَكْرَمَنِیْ بِمَعْرِفَتِهٖ وَمَعْرِفَۃِ رَسُوْلِهٖ وَمَنْ فَرَضَ عَلَیَّ طَاعَتَهٗ رَحْمَۃً مِّنْهُ لِیْ وَتَطَوُّلًا مِنْهُ عَلَیَّ وَمَنَّ عَلَیَّ بِالْاِیْمَانِ۔ اَلْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِیْ اَدْخَلَنِیْ حَرَمَ اَخِیْ رَسُوْلِهٖ وَاَرَانِیْهِ فِیْ عَافِیَۃٍ۔ اَلْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِیْ جَعَلَنِیْ مِنْ زُوَّارِ قَبْرِ وَصِیِّ رَسُوْلِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013182, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, alone without having any associate, and I bear witness that Muhammad is His servant and Messenger. He has conveyed the truth from Allah. And I bear witness that Ali is the servant of Allah and the brother of Allah’s Messenger. Allah is the Most Great. Allah is the Most Great. Allah is the Most Great. There is no god but Allah, and Allah is the Most Great. All praise be to Allah for He has guided me and led me successfully to His course to which He has invited (us).", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai gawahi deta hu keh Allah ke siwaaye koi ma’bood nahi jo yakta hai, koi Uska shareek nahi aur mai gawahi deta hu keh Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) uske bande wa Rasool hai, woh Khuda ki taraf se haq le kar aaye hai aur mai gawahi deta hu keh Ali (a.s) Khuda ke bande aur Rasool'e Khuda (s.a.w.a) ke bhai hai. Allah buzurg-tar hai, Allah buzurg-tar hai, Allah buzurg-tar hai, Allah ke siwaaye koi ma’bood nahi aur Allah buzurg-tar hai, hamd Khuda ke liye hai keh jis ne apne deen ki hidaayat wa taufiq di, jis ki taraf us ne bulaaya.", "Urdu": "میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ اللہ کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں جو یکتا ہے کوئی اس کا شریک نہیں اور میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ حضرت محمدؐ اس کے بندے و رسولؐ ہیں وہ خدا کی طرف سے حق لے کر آئے ہیں اور میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ علیؑ خدا کے بندے اور رسول ِؐخدا کے بھائی ہیں اللہ بزرگ تر ہے اللہ بزرگ تر ہے اللہ بزرگ تر ہے اللہ کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں اور اللہ بزرگ تر ہے حمد خدا کے لئے ہے کہ جس نے اپنے دین کی ہدایت و توفیق دی جس کی طرف اس نے بلایا۔", "RArabic": "ASH-HADO AN LAA ILAAHA ILLALLAA-HO WAHDA-HU LAA SHAREE-KA LAHU WA ASH-HADO ANNA MOHAMMADAN AB’DOHU WA RASOOLO-HU JAAA-A BIL HAQQE MIN IN’DIL-LAAHE WA ASH-HADO ANNA A’LIYYAN AB’DULLAA-HE WA AKHOO RASOO-LIL LAAHE. ALLAAHO AKBARO ALLAAHO AKBARO ALLAAHO AKBARO LAA ILAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WALLAA-HO AKBARO WAL HAMDO LILLAA-HE A’LAA HEDAAYATE-HI WA TAW-FEEQE-HI LEMAA DA’AA ILAIY-HE MIN SABEELE-HI.", "ArabicText1": "اَشْهَدُ اَنْ لَّا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَحْدَهٗ لَا شَرِیْكَ لَهٗ وَ اَشْهَدُ اَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهٗ وَ رَسُوْلُهٗ جَآءَ بِالْحَقِّ مِنْ عِنْدِ اللهِ وَاَشْهَدُ اَنَّ عَلِیًّا عَبْدُ اللهِ وَاَخُوْ رَسُوْلِ اللهِ۔ اَللهُ اَكْبَرُ اَللهُ اَكْبَرُ اَللهُ اَكْبَرُ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَاللهُ اَكْبَرُ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلهِ عَلٰی هِدَایَتِهٖ وَتَوْفِیْقِهٖ لِمَا دَعَا اِلَیْهِ مِنْ سَبِیْلِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013183, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, You are verily the most excellent besought One and the most honorable purposed One. I thus have come to You, seeking nearness to You in the name of Your Prophet, the Prophet of Mercy and in the name of his brother, the Commander of the Faithful, Ali the son of Abu Talib, peace be upon them both. So, (please do) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad, do not disappoint my efforts, (please) grant me a merciful look from You through which You refresh me, make me illustrious in Your view in this world as well as the world to come, and make me of those brought near to You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Be-shak Tu sab se bada matloob aur woh behtareen hai jis ke paas aaya jaata hai aur mai Teri khidmat mein haazir huwa qurb ke liye, ba-waasta Tere Nabi ke jo Nabiye rehmat hai aur ba-waasta unke bhai Ameerul Momeneen Ali ibne Abi Talib (a.s) ke, salaam ho un dono par, pas Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par rehmat farma aur meri yeh koshish na-kaam na bana, nazr farma mujh par maher-baani ki nazr, keh jis se Tu mujhe sahaara de aur mujhe duniya o aakherat mein apne nazdik izzat-daar aur apne muqarra-been (qareeb waalo’n) mein qaraar de.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! بے شک تو سب سے بڑا مطلوب اوروہ بہترین ہے جس کے پاس آیا جاتا ہے اور میں تیری خدمت میں حاضر ہوا قربت کے لئے تیرے نبی ؐکے وسیلے سےجو نبیؐ رحمت ہیں اور ان کے بھائی امیرالمومنین علی ؑ ابن ابی طالبؑ کے واسطے سےسلام ہو ان دونوں پر پس محمدؐ و آل محمدؑپر رحمت فرما اور میری یہ کوشش ناکام نہ بنا، نظرفرما مجھ پر مہربانی کی نظر کہ جس سے تو مجھے سنبھال دے اور مجھے دنیا و آخرت میں اپنے نزدیک عزّت دار اور اپنے مقربین میں قرار دے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNA-KA AFZA-LO MAQSOO-DIN WA AKRA-MO MAA-TIYYIN WA QAD ATAIY-TOKA MOTA-QARRE-BAN ILAIY-KA BE-NABIYYE-KA NABIYYIR RAHMATE WA BE-AKHEE-HE AMEERIL MOMENEENA A’LIYYIBNE ABEE TAALEBIN A’LAIHE-MAS SALAAMO FASALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WA LAA TOKHAYYIB SA’YEE WANZUR ILAIYYA NAZ-RATAN RAHEE-MATAN TAN-A’SHONEE BEHAA WAJ-AL’NEE IN’DAKA WAJEE-HAN FID DUNYAA WAL AAKHE-RATE WA MENAL MOQARRA-BEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّكَ اَفْضَلُ مَقْصُوْدٍ وَاَكْرَمُ مَاْتِیٍّ وَقَدْ اَتَیْتُكَ مُتَقَرِّبًا اِلَیْكَ بِنَبِیِّكَ نَبِیِّ الرَّحْمَۃِ وَبِاَخِیْهِ اَمِیْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ عَلِیِّ بْنِ اَبِیْطَالِبٍ عَلَیْهِمَا السَّلَامُ فَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَلَا تُخَیِّبْ سَعْیِیْ وَانْظُرْ اِلَیَّ نَظْرَۃً رَّحِیْمَۃً تَنْعَشُنِیْ بِهَا وَاجْعَلْنِیْ عِنْدَكَ وَجِیْهًا فِیْ الدُّنْیَا وَالْاٰخِرَۃِ وَمِنَ الْمُقَرَّبِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGr